query:
SELECT p.id, p.apiId, p.ourPrice, p.quantityAvailable, a.name as apiName
FROM prices p
LEFT JOIN sms_apis a ON p.apiId = a.id
WHERE p.serviceId = (SELECT id FROM services WHERE smshubCode = 'wa' LIMIT 1)
  AND p.countryId = 1
ORDER BY p.apiId
